Task Management
=======================

create <task_name>
  Creates a new task

delete <task_name>
  Deletes a task

use <task_name>
  Switches active task to the one specified

using
  Reports the name of the current active task


The Clock
=======================

start
  Starts the clock for the active task

stop
  Stops the clock for the active task

switch
  Stops the clock (if a task is selected and the clock is running) and switches the active task to another task


Reporting
=======================

status
  Reports the current time elapsed for the active task

report
  Reports hours for all tasks


Other
=======================

exit
  Quits the program
